<title>HURSELEY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuni'n Pathien ni a hung tung,
 Amah chawian din I kikhawm;
 Zinga tho in Amah I ho,
 Lawp takin kipahna zie hen.

[V2]
 2. I gitlohnau thupha chawiin,
 Eihaw'n thu gilo I zawp sek;
 Amah lungsiet zie ngaihtuoh in,
 Ei hawih ziek hin mak I sau ui.

[V3]
 3. Ni gup sungin na I sem thei,
 Pathien ni'n sep loh ding ahi;
 Aman A phatna'n ei vuk zel,
 Zie ziekchun Chawlhni A umsak.

[V4]
 4. I lunggil un thu mai mai haw,
 Van lam thu lochuh ngai ki hen;
 Pathien thiengtho A lopi zie,
 Ngaihtuoh zaw hen a pawm tak ahi.

[V5]
 5. Isu guola thilpha bawlin,
 Amah guola thu gen theihna'n;
 Thagau Thieng, Lalpa, ka ngen ui,
 Van chawlhna a ei pui dingin.</lyrics>
</song>